                <h2>
                    <span class="icon-enhanced">
                        <i class="octicon octicon-mark-github" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </span>
                    Part 1: GitHub Setup
                    <span class="badge badge-secondary">10:20-11:00</span>
                </h2>
                <ol>
                    <li><strong>Create GitHub Account</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Go to <a href="https://github.com/signup" target="_blank">Sign up for GitHub</a></li>
                            <li>Use a professional username</li>
                            <li>Add your real name to your profile</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Fork the Course Workspace</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Go to <a href="https://github.com/sicxz/DESN368-code-design-workspace" target="_blank">Course Workspace Repository</a></li>
                            <li>Click "Fork" button (top right)</li>
                            <li>Rename to: <code>desn368-yourname</code></li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                    <li><strong>Make Your First Edit</strong>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Click on README.md</li>
                            <li>Click pencil icon to edit</li>
                            <li>Add your name and save (commit)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </li>
                </ol>

            </section>

            <div class="section-divider"></div>

            <section class="card accent-block card-enhanced">
                <h2>
                    <span class="icon-enhanced">
                        <i class="octicon octicon-tools" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </span>
                    Part 2: Essential Tools
                    <span class="badge badge-secondary">11:10-11:50</span>
                </h2>

