                    <li>‚úÖ Submit your GitHub repository URL to Canvas</li>
                </ul>

                <h3>Optional Exploration:</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Install VS Code extensions (Live Server, Prettier)</li>
                    <li>Apply for Figma Education account</li>
                    <li>Start FreeCodeCamp HTML module</li>
                    <li>Explore Chrome DevTools on your favorite website</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Common Issues & Solutions</h2>
                <div style="padding: 1rem; background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; margin: 1rem 0;">
                    <strong>Can't find the Fork button?</strong><br>
                    Make sure you're logged into GitHub first.
                </div>
                <div style="padding: 1rem; background: #fff3cd; border-left: 4px solid #ffc107; margin: 1rem 0;">
